00:19:52.192 --> 00:19:54.819 position:50% align:center
Well, I found it in our closet.

00:20:01.034 --> 00:20:03.995 position:50% align:center
[HIME] It was in the
ten-years-old box!

00:20:06.581 --> 00:20:09.000 position:50% align:center
Did you look in any
of the other boxes?

00:20:09.084 --> 00:20:10.502 position:50% align:center
Just up until ten.

00:20:10.585 --> 00:20:13.004 position:50% align:center
'Cause that's how old
I am right now.

00:20:13.088 --> 00:20:16.257 position:50% align:center
I'm so excited,
it goes up to 16!

00:20:16.341 --> 00:20:17.884 position:50% align:center
I see.

00:20:17.967 --> 00:20:20.136 position:50% align:center
Daddy? Will you make me
a dress next?

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:23.640 position:50% align:center
Huh? Me?
I, uh... Sure, why not?

00:20:23.723 --> 00:20:25.975 position:50% align:center
Really? Can you sew anything?

00:20:26.059 --> 00:20:28.144 position:50% align:center
Like... Can you
make me some shoes?

00:20:28.228 --> 00:20:29.145 position:50% align:center
Some shoes?

00:20:29.229 --> 00:20:30.897 position:50% align:center
Or sew me some glasses?

00:20:30.980 --> 00:20:34.025 position:50% align:center
Glasses aren't something
you can really sew, Hime.

00:20:34.109 --> 00:20:35.777 position:50% align:center
Uh. Yeah, I knew that!

00:20:35.860 --> 00:20:38.530 position:50% align:center
I just thought you could
because you're so amazing.

00:20:38.613 --> 00:20:41.533 position:50% align:center
But you don't need them.
Your eyesight's fine.

00:20:41.616 --> 00:20:45.161 position:50% align:center
I meant fashion glasses!
You wouldn't understand, Daddy.

00:20:45.245 --> 00:20:47.080 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI laughs]

00:20:49.124 --> 00:20:50.250 position:50% align:center
What brought this on?

00:20:50.333 --> 00:20:53.461 position:50% align:center
Why'd you need me to
teach you how to sew?

00:20:53.545 --> 00:20:55.213 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI]
No reason.

00:21:11.396 --> 00:21:13.815 position:50% align:center
Looks like she
finally found out.

00:21:13.898 --> 00:21:16.151 position:50% align:center
Were you the one who
gave her the key, Rasuna?

00:21:16.234 --> 00:21:22.365 position:50% align:center
[RASUNA] Of course not. It's not
my place to give it to her.

00:21:22.449 --> 00:21:23.742 position:50% align:center
[SATSUKI]
I'm just surprised he was able

00:21:23.825 --> 00:21:25.326 position:50% align:center
to keep it a secret for so long.

00:21:25.410 --> 00:21:29.789 position:50% align:center
[RASUNA] Although... It's not
as if she tried to find out.

00:21:29.873 --> 00:21:34.044 position:50% align:center
[HIME] It was in Kamakura that I
discovered my father's secret.

00:21:34.127 --> 00:21:36.796 position:50% align:center
That he drew manga for a living.

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:39.883 position:50% align:center
And I realized
something else, too.

00:21:39.966 --> 00:21:43.887 position:50% align:center
[HIME] My father may
have hid this from me,

00:21:43.970 --> 00:21:47.057 position:50% align:center
but I also never
tried to uncover it.

00:21:50.560 --> 00:21:56.649 position:50% align:center
[HIME] Maybe, deep down, I was
too scared to know the truth.

00:21:56.733 --> 00:21:59.611 position:50% align:center
Because if I found
out about his job,

00:21:59.694 --> 00:22:01.613 position:50% align:center
then I might discover
more things.

00:22:01.696 --> 00:22:03.531 position:50% align:center
Things I didn't want to know.

00:22:03.615 --> 00:22:07.952 position:50% align:center
And the happy life I shared
with him might disappear.

00:22:08.036 --> 00:22:09.412 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:22:12.749 --> 00:22:17.087 position:50% align:center
[HIME] And then I found
some boxes, within a box.

00:23:47.719 --> 00:23:50.138 position:50% align:center
[KAKUSHI] I have to be able to
run a hundred meters super-fast.

00:23:50.221 --> 00:23:52.098 position:50% align:center
Otherwise they'll know
I'm a manga artist!

00:23:52.182 --> 00:23:53.600 position:50% align:center
[AMI] Those involved
with the way of manga

00:23:53.683 --> 00:23:56.061 position:50% align:center
should only train their muscles
using the way of manga.

00:23:56.144 --> 00:23:56.978 position:50% align:center
[MARIO]
Magnificent!